{"tid":1451663,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"勇武前，請俾dd時間個社會。","createTime":"2019-08-11T19:56:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T04:15:16.000Z","uid":51171,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"527230f27c9cacf93dc219a3f76749549a7835b2","tid":1451663,"uid":51171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:56:07.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: blue;\">俾啲啲時間個社會知道今日發生咩事</span>，<span style=\"color: red;\">同埋醞釀個憤怒嘅氣氛(全民ot做文宣，煲大佢！！)。</span><br />\n<br />\n聽日機場如果要搞，可以搞，但請將811今晚發生嘅所有震撼嘅事擺上枱！一定要！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原因：第二日即衝嘅話，全世界個焦點就去左衝擊到，變相就幫左對家手。社會未反應得切811。<br />\n<br />\n目的：唔係個個都咁updated，俾啲時間佢地去接收資訊(所以文宣要煲得勁啲)，等個社會醞釀氣氛，睇下可唔可以搞到個更大嘅罷工/遊行示威之類。<br />\n即使搞唔成，民間呢股怒氣、呢個氛圍，[black]<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">對緊接下來嘅勇武提供左一個好大嘅support</span></ins></strong>[/black](起碼個社會知你點解咁嬲、點解會升級先)。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">811今晚發生嘅每一件震撼嘅事，文宣煲大佢，唔好靠人做！自己都可以做！<br />\n- 將所有震撼嘅相&amp;片送上wechat、whatsapp嘅洪流！<br />\n- 街招<br />\n- 社交媒體share post<br />\n- 用口傳</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"62fbb1d31d5f623c51442bb93a333cfe142b82ae","tid":1451663,"uid":182575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:57:33.000Z","msg":"好 真係dd㗎咋"},{"pid":"c65d63a86839056e429774d69dcbbca1815df870","tid":1451663,"uid":266601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:00:02.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">721元朗恐襲第23日<br />\n警黑合作<br />\n無人落charge<br />\n無警停職<br />\n葉虎失蹤<br />\n<br />\n無忘721<br />\n記者請日日問</div></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"6650b8545c3d5c77f1e6a519e8b2515f459ae001","tid":1451663,"uid":279650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:09:00.000Z","msg":"不要說推，請說<br />\n721<br />\n811<br />\n1. 尖沙咀瞄頭射，射爆女仕眼球<br />\n2. 以化學武器攻擊葵芳/太古車站內<br />\n3. 北角無視黑幫攻擊記者/平民<br />\n4. 非公職時參與非法集會，以磚/汽油彈攻擊防暴警犬，煽動民眾<br />\n5. 製造偽証<br />\n6. 警犬在太古站推人落電梯"},{"pid":"0c3916afcd326d79ecd5ef44c60f38ca5683f355","tid":1451663,"uid":164420,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:10:27.000Z","msg":"Agree，群眾既怒火要醞釀，但應該一星期就夠。"},{"pid":"32b6e55539be81c60b5b8b1b030bb676b79de13d","tid":1451663,"uid":51171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0c3916afcd326d79ecd5ef44c60f38ca5683f355","tid":1451663,"uid":164420,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:10:27.000Z","msg":"Agree，群眾既怒火要醞釀，但應該一星期就夠。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:11:39.000Z","msg":"係，所以話『dd』<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n全民ot做文宣呀"},{"pid":"b3d23ed2761fbe5ee80c3751e74c06125e30c005","tid":1451663,"uid":99820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:13:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7baead0d0d708578c81f73bf00999a3a2b510393","tid":1451663,"uid":51171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"62fbb1d31d5f623c51442bb93a333cfe142b82ae","tid":1451663,"uid":182575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T19:57:33.000Z","msg":"好 真係dd㗎咋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:17:31.000Z","msg":"ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d300303e8af3ead7e89c5acbea109a1ec99b3e20","tid":1451663,"uid":289620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:19:08.000Z","msg":"真 勇氣請先休息 抖足啲 我地需要你"},{"pid":"1c4e5a2766a5d957bec04d0fb5cec82bf502f4f2","tid":1451663,"uid":52609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:20:37.000Z","msg":"同意，8月16/17/18號，啲狗會終生難忘"},{"pid":"6b969742f5cda0a67a2991fb8d9df2b184133fdc","tid":1451663,"uid":269975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T20:33:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-tWasHlig5s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-tWasHlig5s&d=926QiOG7cNu1sWdYPFF%2FaPUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=b3694111\" da